## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of studies reviewed. The findings are based on general trends and may not account for individual variations within socioeconomic groups. Additionally, the impact of socioeconomic status on learning can be influenced by other intersecting factors such as race, gender, and geographic location, which were not extensively covered in this report.

